1. SetUp

Terminal - first setup environment
1) python -m venv venv
2) venv\Scripts\activate
3) pip install "fastapi[standard]"
4) Pip install uvicorn

Now create a folder app/main.py 
Write some hello world code and try to do this

5) uvicorn app.main:app --reload 


2)  Features

  1) Automatic - Documentation - if we just go to http://127.0.0.1:8000/docs  here /docs will give us swagger api built in so its so easy for development
            - Swagger api - /docs
            - ReDoc api - /redoc


- Security Authentication
- Dependency Injection
- Testing 100% Coverage

3) GET Method overview

- Path Variables = Path variables are values passed directly inside the URL path.
- Predefined Values = You can restrict a path variable to predefined options.
- Query Parameters = Query parameters are added after ? in the URL.

